ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce et d'industrie Saint-Eustache, Deux-Montagnes, Sainte-Marthe-sur-le-Lac (Quebec) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE ET D'INDUSTRIE SAINT-EUSTACHE, DEUX-MONTAGNES, SAINTE-MARTHE-SUR-LE-LAC, in Quebec, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from Saint-Eustache, Deux-Montagnes, Sainte-Marthe-sur-le-Lac to the MRC of Deux-Montagnes which includes Saint-Eustache, Deux-Montagnes, Sainte-Marthe-sur-le-Lac, Saint-Joseph-du-Lac, Pointe-Calumet, Oka et Saint-Placide.
